  "texts": [
    "Each variant in the Fit4Function distribution was represented by either two or six codon replicates; AAV9 was represented by two codon replicates.",
    "The purified AAV library was injected intravenously at a dose of 4.6 × 10 12 vg/kg into a 3.4 kg adult female cynomolgus macaque that was pre-screened for neutralizing antibodies (NAb) against AAV9 (CRL).",
    "Four hours after systemic delivery, the animal was sedated with an intramuscular injection of a combination of ketamine hydrochloride and acepromazine, and anesthetized by a mixture of isoflurane and oxygen.",
    "Next, the animal was perfused with 0.9% sodium chloride, and tissues were harvested and snap-frozen on dry ice.",
    "DNA was extracted using a DNeasy kit in a Qiagen QIAcube Connect."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}